  "entrance_narration": [
    "[color=#6cb4c4][b]The Welcome Wench[/b][/color]\nYou push open the heavy oak door and warmth floods over you \u2014 the crackle of the hearth, the rich smell of roasted meat, and a low hum of conversation fill the crowded common room.",
    "A large [color=#d9a066]carpet[/color] covers the center of the floor, surrounded by tables and chairs. [color=#d9d566]Barkeep Marta[/color] stands behind the polished bar, wiping down a mug. [color=#d9d566]Old Tom[/color] nurses an ale at a corner table. Through a half-open door to the east, a [color=#d9d566]hooded figure[/color] sits alone in a private booth. A [color=#d9d566]quest board[/color] on the far wall catches your eye."
  ]
